{"tid":1613772,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[訂旗]購買光復旗/自訂旗幟攻略","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T19:15:27.000Z","uid":189077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a010f68b98f37a2b6f0b11109921009e7e696a6e","tid":1613772,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"[代朋友出post]<br />\n小小廢話先，個網係美國專賣手工品平台。23/9我落order，問佢係1/10前到唔到香港，呢間shop好好人將我個order好快搞掂由美國寄埋黎香港，終於係30/9到手。<br />\n千其唔好去Amazon訂，好多係大陸廠，DLLM。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>傳送門</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/hk-en/listing/114240925/custom-flags-custom-flag-golf-flags?ref=hp_rv-1&amp;frs=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fhk-en%2Flisting%2F114240925%2Fcustom-flags-custom-flag-golf-flags%3Fref%3Dhp_rv-1%26frs%3D1&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=746c1132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.etsy.com/hk-en/listing/114240925/custom-flags-custom-flag-golf-flags?ref=hp_rv-1&amp;frs=1</a><br />\n<br />\n我就訂左2張3'*5'旗s HKD$300左右，之後寄香港要加多HKD$80 左右運費。Total唔洗400就有2張旗。（望下你屋企既地磚就知3*5有幾大，其實訂2*3都夠）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>步驟</strong><br />\n落order比錢<br />\nsend你想要既圖案比佢，圖越高像素越好<br />\n之後傾個design同output，比多次運費就完<br />\n1-2個星期左右就由DHL去到你手<br />\n<br />\n知你班友仔懶同唔想打咁多英文，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終整懶人包</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.etsystatic.com/icm/4ffcff/218227414/icm_fullxfull.218227414_gnehucppotcggw48wk40.jpg?version=0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.etsystatic.com%2Ficm%2F4ffcff%2F218227414%2Ficm_fullxfull.218227414_gnehucppotcggw48wk40.jpg%3Fversion%3D0&h=9334ff95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直接send 呢張圖比佢地就明架啦，店主話如果多人訂呢款會考慮直接上架。<br />\n<br />\n一張攞出去用，另一張掛去晾衫架。我希望10月底去邊到都見到光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"bd45ec6c1f3a2b73d6357562a17d6de4e88684af","tid":1613772,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"我們都是護旗手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e967da3637c7201412e5ddb54a8bc411f9ded34d","tid":1613772,"uid":205378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">會再出港島既希望你肯花5分鐘睇睇</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【長文】✰✰ 一個港島街坊有野想同今日港島班前線講 ✰✰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egoQGS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egoQGS</a>"},{"pid":"c722da1250514610131642cfe0132931cdbe90b5","tid":1613772,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a246d292e450707d1470b84c4236b1d9e6f4927a","tid":1613772,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"我們都是護旗手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7955f54c84f5e2418f456edfe4f076a800ec472","tid":1613772,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"整英文"},{"pid":"63ed76bca8539c1af255a76abd4615c15e9b1864","tid":1613772,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7955f54c84f5e2418f456edfe4f076a800ec472","tid":1613772,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"整英文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T